## 第三部分：字节流读写示例

### 3.1 写入文件（FileOutputStream + BufferedOutputStream）

```java
public static void fileOutputStream() throws IOException {
    String str = "hello world!";
    File file = new File("d:\\test2.txt");  // 创建文件对象
    
    if (!file.exists()) {
        file.createNewFile();  // 文件不存在则创建
    }
    
    FileOutputStream fOutputStream = new FileOutputStream(file);
    BufferedOutputStream bOutputStream = new BufferedOutputStream(fOutputStream);
    
    byte[] buffer = str.getBytes();  // 字符串 → 字节数组
    bOutputStream.write(buffer);
    
    bOutputStream.close();  // 先关外层
    fOutputStream.close();  // 再关内层
}
```

### 3.2 读取文件（FileInputStream + BufferedInputStream）

```java
public static void fileInput() throws IOException {
    File file = new File("d:\\test2.txt");
    FileInputStream finput = new FileInputStream(file);
    BufferedInputStream bfinput = new BufferedInputStream(finput);
    
    int temp = 0;
    while ((temp = bfinput.read()) != -1) {  // -1 表示读取完毕
        System.out.print((char) temp);
    }
    
    bfinput.close();
    finput.close();
}
```

### 3.3 字节流复制文件

```java
import java.io.FileInputStream;
import java.io.FileOutputStream;
import java.io.IOException;

public class CopyBytes {
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        FileInputStream in = null;
        FileOutputStream out = null;
        
        try {
            in = new FileInputStream("xanadu.txt");
            out = new FileOutputStream("outagain.txt");
            
            int c;
            while ((c = in.read()) != -1) {
                out.write(c);  // 逐字节复制
            }
        } finally {
            if (in != null) in.close();
            if (out != null) out.close();
        }
    }
}
```

